data.description: Welcome to your captivating 4-bedroom, 2-bath castle in a vibrant community with top-notch schools, local shops, and nearby parks and churches. This haven of modern living boasts recent upgrades, including flooring, paint, kitchen, lighting, plumbing, AC, and more. A unique exterior door in one bedroom creates an ideal space for a home office or retreat. Entertain on the covered porch, seamlessly transitioning to the multi-use workshop area with a roll-up door. In the backyard, a well-equipped portable building offers endless possibilities for hobbies, a home gym, or a secluded oasis. Cut costs effortlessly with recently installed solar panels—all expenses covered. Discover the perfect blend of modern amenities and classic charm in this meticulously updated home. Your dream awaits—seize the opportunity in the vibrant community of Canton!
